Game Info:
~~~~~~~~~~
WORM VS. WORM. It's the end of the worm world as we know it! In Worms Armageddon on Sega Dreamcast, those wriggly pink creatures may look cute, butthey're wreaking havoc underground as they try to bump each other off. Don't let the game's humorous antics, voices, and animations fool you - you need all the strategy and skill you can muster tolead your team to victory. There are dozens of zany weapons at yourdisposal, and some may surprise you such as the exploding Ming Vase, mole bombs, and mad cows falling from the sky. Turn-based,multi-player mode lets you pit your team against up to four others.Single-player mode challenges you with a series of fast and furiousmissions. Who ever said worms were slow?

- Next generation of the smash PC hit Worms 2.
- More than 60 wacky and unexpected weapons. 
- Customize your battle or play on one of the thousands of randomizedlandscapes.
- Multiple ways to play, including campaigns, matches, and training missions. 
- Outlandish 2D graphics and sound bring the worms to life.